  SD:0.25@0.06 SD:0.25@0.2 SD:0.25@0.35 SD:0.25@0.5 SD:0.5@0.64 BD:1.5 SD:1
  >P6
  BD:1 SD:0.5 BD:1.25 BD:0.25 SD:0.25 BD:0.75
